+== Untrusted authenticators and libcbor
+
+pam-u2f applies defense-in-depth measures against malicious or
+malfunctioning FIDO authenticators, including CBOR messages crafted to
+trigger oversized memory allocations in `libcbor`/`libfido2`. See
+link:SECURITY-CONSIDERATIONS.md[] for details.
